org.mini2Dx.core.lock

Interface ReentrantLock

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JvmReentrantLock

    public interface ReentrantLock
    Interface for lock implementations that allow for re-entry. See ReentrantLock for more information on how re-entrant locks work.
